'''巴克哈德·阿卜迪'''（{{lang-en|Barkhad Abdi}}，{{lang-so|Barkhad Cabdi}}，{{lang-ar|برخد عبدي}}，{{bd|1985年|4月10日}}）[[索馬里|索馬里]]裔[[美國|美國]]籍演員及導演，執導過幾部[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]，2013年飾演電影《[[怒海劫|怒海劫]]》中的[[海盜|海盜]]開始為人熟識<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/10/09/barkhad-abdi-forrest-gump_n_4063352.html |title=Barkhad Abdi, 'Captain Phillips' Star, On Growing Up In Somalia To Starring With Tom Hanks<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-03-31 |archive-date=2016-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160728104953/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/10/09/barkhad-abdi-forrest-gump_n_4063352.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=voa>{{cite news|title=Somali-American Actor Stars in 'Captain Phillips' Movie|url=http://www.voanews.com/content/somali-american-actor-stars-in-captain-phillips-movie/1767931.html|accessdate=16 March 2014|newspaper=[[Voice_of_America|Voice of America]]|date=11 October 2013|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070436/http://www.voanews.com/content/somali-american-actor-stars-in-captain-phillips-movie/1767931.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，亦為他帶來數個國際電影獎項的提名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goldenglobes.com/2014/best-supporting-actor-motion-picture |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-01  |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203094724/http://www.goldenglobes.com/2014/best-supporting-actor-motion-picture |archivedate=2014-02-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Rottenberg|first=Josh|title=Oscars 2014: Barkhad Abdi reacts to his Best Supporting Actor nomination|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/01/16/barkhad-abdi-oscars-2014/|publisher=Entertainment Weekly|accessdate=1 February 2014|archive-date=2014-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017031035/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/01/16/barkhad-abdi-oscars-2014/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，當中贏得[[第67屆英國電影學院獎|第67屆英國電影學院獎]][[英國電影學院獎最佳男配角|最佳男配角]]獎。

==個人簡介==
阿卜迪生於[[索馬里|索馬里]]南部[[巴納迪爾州|巴納迪爾州]]城市[[摩加迪沙|摩加迪沙]]，在[[也門|也門]]長大，直到14歲隨家人移民[[美國|美國]]，在[[明尼蘇達州|明尼蘇達州]][[明尼阿波利斯|明尼阿波利斯]]居住。當演員之前，他曾經在兄長的店舖內售賣[[手提電話|手提電話]]<ref name="Tnytpc">{{cite news|last=Goodyear|first=Dana|title=The Pictures - Contender|url=http://archives.newyorker.com/?i=2014-03-03#folio=026|accessdate=6 March 2014|newspaper=[[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]]|date=3 March 2014|archive-date=2018-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181203055500/http://archives.newyorker.com/?i=2014-03-03#folio=026|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亦曾經當過[[加长轿车|加长轿车]]的[[司機|司機]]。《怒海劫》的角色為他帶來了6萬5千美元的收入<ref>[http://movies.yahoo.com/news/oscar-nominee-barkhad-abdi-far-rich-captain-phillips-215653200.html ‘Captain Phillips’ Oscar Nominee Barkhad Abdi Is Broke] {{Wayback|url=http://movies.yahoo.com/news/oscar-nominee-barkhad-abdi-far-rich-captain-phillips-215653200.html |date=20140314141801 }} Yahoo via TheWrap.com</ref>，拍攝完畢隨即返回兄長的店舖工作。

